\mathbb R^n
c_k
x=\sum_{k=1}^n c_kv_k
(x|v_i)=\left(\sum_{k=1}^n c_kv_k{\Huge |}v_i\right) = \sum_{k=1}^n c_k(v_k|v_i) = c_i \|v_i\|^2=c_i
\|v_i\|=1
(v_k|v_i)=0
